CPAN Power Tools

A two part presentation on creating distributions.

Part I: CPAN distributions.
Part II: Using the CPAN tools for private distributions.


Files:

CPAN-Power-Tools-Talk.odf	Libre Office Impress document.
public/Power-Tools-I.htm	Starting point for HTML version of presentation.
myapp.pl			Mojolicious Lite-App for HTML version.
public/*.html			Individual slides.
public/*.png			Graphics for slides and navigation buttons.


The .odf format is the native presentation format.

To use the HTML format:
morbo myapp.pl

Then point a browser at server.ip.address:3000

Enjoy!

